{"type":"message","id":"1f5e807e","parentId":"e2808d2c","timestamp":"2026-03-18T14:07:01.714Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"很好！现在我需要等待尚书省返回执行结果。根据门下省的回复，它已经转交尚书省执行了。\n\n我应该等待尚书省的 subagent 返回结果。让我稍等一下，看看是否有结果回来。\n\n根据门下省的回复：\"已转交尚书省执行。\"，尚书省应该在处理任务了。\n\n让我检查一下尚书省的 session 状态：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0becef18c54d47198f3a4693","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw && openclaw sessions --agent shangshu --active 5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai_zhongshu","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":33,"output":192,"cacheRead":22554,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22779,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773842818188}}
